Make sure you have this packages installed on your system:

  autoconf 
  libtool 
  libx11-dev 
  pkg-config 
  libxrender-dev 
  libxtst-dev 
  libxml2-dev

Building & installing from source tarball:

  wget https://sourceforge.net/projects/mygestures/files/latest/download?source=files -O mygestures.tar.xz
  tar xvf mygestures.tar.xz
  cd mygestures-git
  sh autogen.sh
  ./configure
  make
  sudo make install

Building & installing from git ("master" branch)

  git clone git://git.code.sf.net/p/mygestures/git mygestures-git
  cd mygestures-git
  sh autogen.sh
  ./configure
  make
  sudo make install

Hacking mygestures & generating debian&dist packages
  
  git commit -a                  # commit your changes on "master" branch                 
  git checkout -b debian origin/debian # switch to "debian" branch from the origin.
  git merge master               # merge "master" into "debian"
  sh autogen.sh                  
  ./configure
  make
  dpkg-buildpackage  -uc -us     # generate your unsigned packages
  ls -l ../mygestures_*          # list generated packages
  
